Package: pharmaOncoX
Type: Package
Title: Annotated targeted and non-targeted anticancer drugs
Version: 0.9.1
Date: 2022-08-31
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Sigve",
             family = "Nakken",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "sigven@ifi.uio.no",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8468-2050")))
Maintainer: Sigve Nakken <sigven@ifi.uio.no>
Description: This data package collects aticancer drug information from multiple resources,
    including Open Targets Platform/ChEMBL, NCI Thesaurus, and PubChem. The main dataset
    contains a list of all anticancer drugs per indication/tumor type (where this is provided),
    which can be queried with a range of parameters (minimum clinical phase, approval
    status, targets, drug category etc.)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/sigven/pharmaOncoX
